    "Description": {
      "type": "text",
      "dtype": "String",
      "label": "Metapower Description",
      "value": "<p align=\"center\"><em><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">Gravitational Pull is a more focused technique within the Control Gravity arsenal. By creating a gravitational epicenter within a targeted area, you can cause an abrupt shift in the local gravitational forces. Individuals in proximity to the epicenter will be irresistibly drawn toward it, as if the very earth itself craves their presence. The strongest among them might resist the pull, but most will be inexorably drawn toward the epicenter's heart. Skillful Controllers can extend the reach of this effect, targeting additional, and heavier targets and even employing it from a distance. Yet, a mistimed attempt could result in the Controller inadvertently becoming the epicenter of the gravitational pull, briefly tethered to the ground.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"
